Dear Carl:     
As a reader, friend, & publisher of bp Nichol's, I'm glad to have you   
here. I encourage you to bring nichol issues out here, as I believe his     
is a poetics vastly undervalued in America, if not in Canada, and that  
his various approaches to theory, poetics, and writing involve a joy    
which is rare and needed.     
    
    charles alexander     
