CALL FOR PAPERS    
    
The Graduate Student Caucus of the MLA will sponsor a session at the 1995   
convention called  
    
CONVERSE BETWEEN CRITIC-WRITER AND WRITER-CRITIC     
    
How seriously can critical theorists take creative writers as theorists?    
How seriously should creative writers take critics as creative writers?     
Critical and creatve responses by or about creative writers and critics     
sought. 1-2 page abstracts to -   
    
Joe Aimone     
Dept of English    
University of California, Davis   
