Dear Tony Green:   
    
If you want to define theory that broadly, then we have less 
argument--none in terms as you've extended my statement about       
"anticipation." I personally think this is where poetics and theory don't   
overlap. Where poetics is but theory isn't would be the most necessary  
area to me--and the least dangerous.  
    
Spencer    
