"theory" out (I stand corrected). It's not in SPD's catalog; it was a   
mimeo or Xeroxed & stapled book that (maybe) Duncan McNaughton published.   
Whether or not copies are still available's uncertain. Stephen Ratcliffe,   
do you know?   
    
