Subject:  digesting poetics   
    
To all those worried about cluttered mailboxes: have you tried the      
"digest" option?  The discussion does feel a little less "live" &   
somewhat more "archived," but it certainly helps to receive only one    
"message" per day rather than 30.  It also makes it possible for me     
to print the whole thing out as one file if I get tired of perusing     
pixels.    
    
On the other hand, it's a lot easier for a day or days to slip by w/out     
me getting around to poetics stuff at all.  I guess my personal jury is     
still out, but i'd recommend that people give it a shot to see if it    
alleviates their particular difficulties with navigating the infopoglut.    
    
steve shoemaker    
