Subject:  correction      
    
Subject: AHP Correction on Lean Times Story      
Copyright: 1999 by The Anti-Hegemony Project     
Date: 31 Feb 99 26:30:13 PST      
    
Lines: 7   
    
    LOS ANGELES (AHP) -- In a story yesterday about a study examining   
how shortages of inspired language and increasing population will affect    
U.S. poetics production and Americans' diet of subsidized corn porn lyrics, 
The Anti-Hegemony project erroneously reported the corporate affiliation    
of a researcher.   
    Marjorie Perloff is employed by Lang-Po Labs, not Arithmetrick  
Frozen Yogurt Co. Down Under.     
